# dev-nvim Demo Scripts
#
# Individual demos are in the demo/ directory:
#
#   demo-overview.tape      - Which-key, cheatsheet (8s)
#   demo-navigation.tape    - File explorer, telescope, buffers (12s)
#   demo-lsp.tape           - Hover docs, go to definition, grep (12s)
#   demo-git.tape           - LazyGit integration (8s)
#   demo-ai-pairing.tape    - Full AI collaboration workflow (25s)
#                             Context copy, auto-reload, diffs, claude-edit
#
# Record all at once:
#   cd demo && ./record-all.sh
#
# Or record individually:
#   cd demo && vhs demo-ai-pairing.tape
